    There was also an extensive port of the Software Tools to VMS, done
    by Joe Sventek at LBNL.   Included at the key tools, the shell,
    pipes, everything.   Felt completely like Unix.<br>
    Deborah<br>
    <br>
    <div class="moz-cite-prefix">On 7/12/19 10:00 AM, Clem Cole wrote:<br>
